I'll go make you some medicine.

00:13:36.280 --> 00:13:36.880
Haiyue,

00:13:40.440 --> 00:13:43.000
if I die this time,

00:13:43.000 --> 00:13:44.120
would you be sad?

00:13:45.880 --> 00:13:46.680
Knock on wood, quick!

00:13:48.640 --> 00:13:50.640
How many times have I told you?

00:13:51.520 --> 00:13:54.000
Don't say unlucky things, don't jinx it.

00:13:55.000 --> 00:13:56.640
Got it. Don't worry.

00:13:57.000 --> 00:13:57.840
I'm not dying.

00:13:58.200 --> 00:13:59.200
I still have to take care of you.

00:14:00.640 --> 00:14:03.680
And there's Jin Zi and Luo Da too.

00:14:05.320 --> 00:14:07.440
Just don't make us worry, that's enough.

00:14:08.680 --> 00:14:09.640
I'll go make you some medicine.

00:14:27.280 --> 00:14:28.280
Shisan is back.

00:14:30.000 --> 00:14:30.680
Shisan,

00:14:31.320 --> 00:14:33.000
don't listen to the rumors outside.

00:14:33.000 --> 00:14:34.680
Saying your uncle plans this or that.

00:14:34.680 --> 00:14:35.840
That's impossible.

00:14:36.560 --> 00:14:38.960
I'm here to help you this time.

00:14:42.400 --> 00:14:44.120
Just like I helped my father back then.

00:14:44.760 --> 00:14:47.280
Just like I helped your father back then.

00:14:56.520 --> 00:14:57.000
Tell me,

00:14:57.840 --> 00:14:59.560
your father was too stubborn back then.

00:14:59.560 --> 00:15:01.400
He never listened to my good advice.

00:15:01.400 --> 00:15:02.320
But you're different.

00:15:02.440 --> 00:15:04.320
You're sensible, nephew.

00:15:04.520 --> 00:15:06.080
If you sell me the Divine Dragon's Twin-Incense Ginseng

00:15:06.080 --> 00:15:07.760
and the Nine Immortals' Compass,

00:15:07.960 --> 00:15:10.400
you'll have endless wealth and glory.

00:15:13.080 --> 00:15:13.960
Not selling.

00:15:14.320 --> 00:15:15.000
Name your price.

00:15:15.440 --> 00:15:16.200
I want your life.

00:15:16.640 --> 00:15:17.840
You're talking like a child again.

00:15:18.280 --> 00:15:19.400
Stop saying things out of anger.

00:15:19.680 --> 00:15:21.280
I'm here with real sincerity.

00:15:21.680 --> 00:15:23.760
I redeemed this for you.

00:15:23.760 --> 00:15:25.200
That was a good deed.

00:15:25.520 --> 00:15:26.640
Jin Ginseng House.

00:15:26.960 --> 00:15:28.400
Liuhe Tang wiped me out.

00:15:28.520 --> 00:15:31.200
Jin Ginseng House is different in your hands.

00:15:31.200 --> 00:15:32.520
You can't put it that way.

00:15:32.520 --> 00:15:34.400
Just sell me these two treasures.

00:15:35.000 --> 00:15:36.080
How much do you want?

00:15:36.080 --> 00:15:37.640
I'll give you whatever you ask.

00:15:37.640 --> 00:15:38.440
The ginseng I've collected—

00:15:38.560 --> 00:15:39.440
if you want it,

00:15:39.440 --> 00:15:40.440
we can go into business together.

00:15:40.640 --> 00:15:43.200
We just need to report to Liuhe Tang together.

00:15:43.400 --> 00:15:45.080
If you want my position, that's fine too.

00:15:45.080 --> 00:15:46.440
You can take over for me.

00:15:46.880 --> 00:15:48.760
From now on, the whole guild

00:15:48.760 --> 00:15:50.000
will answer to the two of us.

00:15:50.200 --> 00:15:50.880
If you want money,

00:15:51.840 --> 00:15:54.320
just say it. I'll give you whatever you want.

00:15:59.320 --> 00:15:59.880
Alright.

00:16:01.400 --> 00:16:04.440
I'll think about the terms tonight.

00:16:04.760 --> 00:16:05.840
I'll give you an answer tomorrow.

00:16:06.440 --> 00:16:08.320
That's all I wanted to hear.

00:16:16.640 --> 00:16:17.440
Shisan,

00:16:18.440 --> 00:16:20.200
I'm waiting for your good news.